name: Space Dash (Skrubtimer)
description: One day, you are captured by alien creatures in a world which is a mash between pixels and squares! Go through the doors, avoid the sizzling lava and try not to get caught by those aliens!  Made for the Unexpected Jam 2020. Music used: "Mark Hutson - Endless void" is under a Creative Commons license (CC BY-SA 3.0) https://creativecommons.org/licenses/... Music promoted by BreakingCopyright: https://youtu.be/4KLpS2nT8nk (If you find that you can't jump click 'Retry Level' :)
